1
00:01:03,610 --> 00:01:05,910
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,190 --> 00:01:09,870
[Episode 19]

3
00:01:31,590 --> 00:01:32,680
Ms. Jiang.

4
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:37,759
What are you doing?

5
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,560
Would you like to take a look?

6
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,610
What are you going to do?

7
00:02:12,470 --> 00:02:14,430
I'm still unfamiliar
with political affairs.

8
00:02:14,430 --> 00:02:16,910
So help me select some books.

9
00:02:35,900 --> 00:02:39,420
[Standards
for Being a Good Pupil and Child]

10
00:02:49,510 --> 00:02:50,880
Did you hide this?

11
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:54,540
Your Highness,

12
00:02:54,640 --> 00:02:56,990
if I had hidden the imperial seal,

13
00:02:57,150 --> 00:03:00,210
wouldn't it be the safest
to hide it outside the palace?

14
00:03:13,090 --> 00:03:14,310
[Auspicious Mists of Grace and Peace]

15
00:03:14,310 --> 00:03:15,120
Nianzhao.

16
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:19,360
This is...

17
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:22,000
I have found the imperial seal.

18
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:24,200
This is the enthronement edict.

19
00:03:31,750 --> 00:03:33,210
So we're about to succeed?

20
00:03:36,870 --> 00:03:39,000
For my smooth ascension to the throne,

21
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:41,450
I still need one crucial trigger.

22
00:03:42,150 --> 00:03:43,360
In other words,

23
00:03:43,630 --> 00:03:45,680
how do you plan to frame Xie Jiuzhao?

24
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,750
It depends on...

25
00:03:50,150 --> 00:03:52,079
how far you're willing to go

26
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,620
for me.

27
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,630
A mother

28
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,400
would naturally do anything

29
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:01,750
for her child.

30
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:09,120
Then please reveal

31
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:13,280
your past affair at court tomorrow.

32
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:14,150
What...

33
00:04:16,510 --> 00:04:18,040
What are you talking about?

34
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:21,600
Before entering the palace,

35
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:24,950
you had already secretly pledged yourself
to Old General Xun

36
00:04:24,950 --> 00:04:27,350
and given birth to his eldest son,
Xun Simo.

37
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:30,240
Now Xun Simo is dead.

38
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:33,130
Xie Jiuzhao's whereabouts are unknown.

39
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:38,360
Why don't we just give him no way out?

40
00:04:39,190 --> 00:04:40,920
Announce to the world

41
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:44,360
that Xie Jiuzhao, like Xun Simo,

42
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:48,600
is your bastard with Old General Xun.

43
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:52,870
Do you want my disgrace...

44
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:56,310
to be known by everyone?

45
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:07,750
Mother.

46
00:05:09,270 --> 00:05:10,750
All these years,

47
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:14,830
I've lived in fear day and night,

48
00:05:15,310 --> 00:05:17,870
wondering what I should do

49
00:05:19,190 --> 00:05:21,120
if my true identity is discovered.

50
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:23,870
I tried to please Xie Jiuzhao every day

51
00:05:23,950 --> 00:05:24,720
because...

52
00:05:25,630 --> 00:05:28,160
only if he acknowledges me
as his true brother

53
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:30,390
can I survive in this palace!

54
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,070
And what have you done?

55
00:05:33,510 --> 00:05:36,270
You've forced me
to compete with him again and again!

56
00:05:36,270 --> 00:05:38,190
But I'm just a bastard

57
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:40,000
of you and an official!

58
00:05:40,800 --> 00:05:42,560
What do I have to compete with him?

59
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,090
That's not true, Nianzhao!

60
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,960
As long as you don't tell anyone,

61
00:05:46,510 --> 00:05:48,800
no one will know.

62
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:58,310
My dear father

63
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:02,190
wrote a letter to Liu Yeqing,

64
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:05,870
revealing the identities
of both me and Xun Simo.

65
00:06:08,310 --> 00:06:11,630
It's now in Jiang Li's hands.

66
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:18,270
Liu Yeqing,

67
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:24,950
why must you haunt me like this?

68
00:06:24,950 --> 00:06:25,870
Mother.

69
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,480
Have you decided?

70
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:45,870
You truly are my good son.

71
00:06:51,390 --> 00:06:52,510
I...

72
00:06:54,240 --> 00:06:55,870
congratulate you...

73
00:06:57,950 --> 00:07:00,360
on getting what you want!

74
00:07:09,470 --> 00:07:17,720
[Auspicious Mists of Grace and Peace]

75
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,680
It's already at this hour.

76
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:48,870
This...

77
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,870
Prince Nianzhao...

78
00:07:49,870 --> 00:07:52,070
is actually wearing the imperial robe?

79
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:55,140
And he brought soldiers here!

80
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:58,050
Why did he bring soldiers to court?

81
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:15,190
This is treason! How dare you!

82
00:08:15,190 --> 00:08:17,600
Prince Nianzhao, you came here
wearing the imperial robe.

83
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:20,390
Are you attempting a rebellion?

84
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,600
Enough.

85
00:08:29,780 --> 00:08:31,380
I brought soldiers to court.

86
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:34,750
It's understandable that you have doubts.

87
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,669
As for why I'm wearing the imperial robe

88
00:08:37,669 --> 00:08:39,440
and sitting on the throne,

89
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,679
I'll let the empress dowager

90
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:45,200
explain everything to you.

91
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:14,480
Prince Nianzhao is sitting there

92
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:18,790
because Xie Jiuzhao, the Crown Prince...

93
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:22,630
is not of royal blood.

94
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:23,680
This is...

95
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:25,910
Impossible.

96
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:33,600
Your Majesty,
do you know what you're saying?

97
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,200
Before I entered the palace,

98
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:39,390
I had an affair with General Xun Chuanmo.

99
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:44,440
Xun Simo is our eldest son.

100
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,870
Xie Jiuzhao...

101
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,750
is our second son.

102
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,150
Then Prince Nianzhao...

103
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:54,600
He's the son of me and the late emperor!

104
00:09:54,600 --> 00:09:56,960
At that time,
I had been in the palace for many years.

105
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:59,910
You all can verify this yourselves.

106
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:06,200
Then why are you
only mentioning this today?

107
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:11,270
The late emperor was assassinated
12 years ago.

108
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:14,270
I knew my sins were grave.

109
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:17,320
I wanted to help Prince Nianzhao
ascend the throne.

110
00:10:17,320 --> 00:10:20,550
However, although the late emperor
already knew everything,

111
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:23,270
out of years of their father-son ties,

112
00:10:23,270 --> 00:10:25,530
he generously spared Xie Jiuzhao and me.

113
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:29,360
He was even reluctant to strip him
of his crown prince status.

114
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:32,000
Unexpectedly, Xun Simo

115
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:34,000
committed treason,

116
00:10:34,120 --> 00:10:36,080
intending to kill Prince Nianzhao

117
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:38,720
to cover up for his brother Xie Jiuzhao!

118
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:44,250
I refuse to continue this wrongdoing.

119
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:47,750
Today, I reveal everything to you all

120
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:53,030
to restore clarity to the royal family.

121
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,480
As a bastard, Xie Jiuzhao

122
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,200
indeed can't inherit the throne.

123
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:01,270
The empress dowager is their birth mother.

124
00:11:01,270 --> 00:11:02,910
If not for a guilty conscience,

125
00:11:02,910 --> 00:11:04,630
either of her two sons being the emperor

126
00:11:04,630 --> 00:11:06,360
would have been the same to her.

127
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:10,210
Prince Nianzhao, please ascend the throne

128
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:12,960
to restore clarity to the royal family!

129
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:15,320
If that's the case,

130
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:19,390
where is Xie Jiuzhao now?

131
00:11:19,750 --> 00:11:23,120
Who will write the enthronement edict?

132
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,720
The traitor Xie Jiuzhao has already fled.

133
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,080
As for the enthronement edict,

134
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:34,600
it was already drafted yesterday.

135
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:39,080
All of you can take a look.

136
00:11:45,230 --> 00:11:45,820
[By Heaven's mandate, a new chapter
of imperial succession is proclaimed.]

137
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:46,500
[The 10th Prince, Nianzhao,
is of royal blood.]

138
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,480
No.

139
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:58,440
The imperial seal's imprint is wrong.

140
00:11:59,150 --> 00:12:03,000
The imperial seal was personally made
by the founding emperor.

141
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:06,390
His empress
was of Western Regions descent.

142
00:12:06,390 --> 00:12:06,490
So a specially crafted inscription

143
00:12:06,490 --> 00:12:08,880
[Xie Jiuzhao, the ninth prince,
is not of royal blood.]

144
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:09,000
[The truth is now revealed to all.
He has deceived Heaven.]

145
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:10,840
was imprinted around the imperial seal.

146
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,080
[In coveting the throne, he's transgressed
all bounds of order and kinship.]

147
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,720
But on this edict,

148
00:12:14,270 --> 00:12:16,910
there's no trace of the inscription.

149
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:21,720
Darn it!

150
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,360
Could it be that Xie Jiuzhao

151
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:25,150
swapped the imperial seal?

152
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,790
Prince Nianzhao,

153
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:30,510
you are destined to rule.

154
00:12:30,670 --> 00:12:33,130
There's no need
to press the matter just yet.

155
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:35,200
You can temporarily oversee state affairs
as regent.

156
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:37,200
When the imperial seal is returned,

157
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:39,630
we can follow Heaven's will
and the people's hearts

158
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:42,750
to select an auspicious day
for the grand succession.

159
00:12:42,750 --> 00:12:45,320
-I second the proposal!
-I second the proposal!
